# Private source tree + dev workspace — kept LOCAL, never published.
# This is the plugin-only public repo; the plugin is built from /src/ off-repo.
/src/
/.claude

# Build artifacts
**/dist/
**/.build-state/

# Personal-judgment notes — fill on local machine, never commit.
# Skill loader gracefully skips when not present.
**/references/judgment-notes.md

# Engagement state files — produced per session, not part of the skill bundle.
**/engagements/
**/engagement-state-*.yaml
**/council-state-*.yaml

# Python
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.egg-info/
.venv/
venv/
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/

# OS / Editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.idea/
.vscode/

# Claude Code session state — ephemeral per-session files the CC harness writes into a
# .claude/ dir at the agent's cwd. Ignore by pattern at any depth; never wholesale **/.claude/
# (that would hide tracked .claude/skills, .claude/agents, settings.json).
**/.claude/context-state.json
**/.claude/context-state.json.tmp
**/.claude/context-state-*.json
**/.claude/recovery.md
**/.claude/recovery-*.md
**/.claude/compact-pending
**/.claude/compact-pending-*
**/.claude/session-files-*.txt
